<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Dry Runner</title>
		<link
			rel="shortcut icon"
			sizes="16px"
			href="/images/icon.png"
			type="image/x-icon"
		/>
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
		<link
			href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300&display=swap"
			rel="stylesheet"
		/>
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			type="text/css"
			href="/plugin/codemirror/lib/codemirror.css"
		/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/home.css" />
		<script
			src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.min.js"
			integrity="sha256-9/aliU8dGd2tb6OSsuzixeV4y/faTqgFtohetphbbj0="
			crossorigin="anonymous"
		></script>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/plugin/codemirror/theme/dracula.css" />
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/plugin/codemirror/theme/duotone-light.css"
		/>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/plugin/codemirror/theme/blackboard.css" />

		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/lib/codemirror.js"></script>
		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/addon/edit/closebrackets.js"></script>
		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/mode/clike/clike.js"></script>
		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/addon/fold/foldcode.js"></script>
		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/addon/fold/foldgutter.js"></script>
		<script src="/plugin/codemirror/addon/fold/brace-fold.js"></script>
		<link
			rel="stylesheet"
			href="/plugin/codemirror/addon/fold/foldgutter.css"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="left-section">
			<div id="heading">
				<img src="/images/icon.png" alt="" />
				<h2>Dry Runner</h2>
			</div>

			<ul class="list-class">
				<li>
					<button class="collapsible">HOW TO USE?</button>
					<div class="content">
						<ul>
							<li>Write or paste your code in the editor</li>
							<li>Enter custom input in bottom right, if any.</li>
							<li>
								Hit the submit button and wait for the magic.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</li>

				<li>
					<button class="collapsible">FEEDBACK</button>
					<div class="content">
						<ul>
							<li>
								Click on feedback button on top right corner.
							</li>
							<li>
								if there is any error in website graphics please
								submit your code.
							</li>
							<li>Your suggestion are always welcome.</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<button class="collapsible">Contribute</button>
					<div class="content">
						<ul>
							<li>You can always improve the website.</li>
							<li>
								Go to github page to chage the code or suggest
								some UI/UX change in suggestion box.
							</li>
							<li>Buy me a course on machine learning</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>

			<div id="helper-buttons">
				<a href=""><img src="/images/feedback.png" alt="" /></a>
				<a href=""><img src="/images/github.png" alt="" /></a>
				<a href=""><img src="/images/donate.png" alt="" /></a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div id="right-section">
			<div id="nav-bar">
				<div class="theme-container">
					<span>Select Theme :</span>
					<select name="theme" id="theme-changer">
						<option value="dracula">dracula</option>
						<option value="duotone-light">duotone-light</option>
						<option value="blackboard">blackboard</option>
					</select>
				</div>

				<div class="language-container">
					<span>Select Language :</span>
					<select name="language" id="language-changer">
						<option value="Java">Java</option>
					</select>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div id="bottom-bar">
				<textarea
					name="custom-input"
					id="custom-input-textarea"
					placeholder="Enter Custom Input"
				></textarea>
				<button id="custom-input" class="bottom-bar-button">
					Custom Input
				</button>
				<button
					id="submit-button"
					class="bottom-bar-button"
					type="submit"
				>
					Submit
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>

		<script src="/js/home.js"></script>
		<script src="/js/styleHandler.js"></script>
	</body>
</html>
